## 代码规范补充 / Additional Coding Rules / コーディング規約の補足

- 每个函数/方法都应有对应的单元测试。
- Every function/method should have a corresponding unit test.

- 每次修改时应将任务分解为小步骤，每次只修改少量内容，自动确认无误后再继续。
- When making changes, break tasks into small steps, modify only a small part each time, and automatically proceed only if this step there are no issues.
